<db:section xml:id="swipeAngle-prop">
<db:title>swipeAngle : qreal</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the angle of the motion associated with the gesture</db:para>
<db:para>If the gesture has either a horizontal or vertical component, the swipe angle describes the angle between the direction of motion and the x-axis as defined using the standard widget <db:link xlink:href="coordsys.xml">coordinate system</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>
<db:emphasis role="bold">Access functions:
</db:emphasis>
</db:para>
